ffmpeg / ffprobe
----------------
The desktop app ships the ffmpeg and ffprobe binaries provided by the
@ffmpeg-installer/ffmpeg and @ffprobe-installer/ffprobe packages, and the web
app uses ffmpeg.wasm. ffmpeg is licensed under the LGPL/GPL depending on build
configuration. These binaries are distributed unmodified. Their source and
license are available from https://ffmpeg.org . If you redistribute Sada
builds, keep this notice and provide access to the corresponding ffmpeg source.

Speech service
--------------
Transcription uses Meta's Wit.ai (https://wit.ai), a free hosted service, via a
user-supplied token. Wit.ai is a service, not bundled code, and is governed by
Meta's own terms.

